title: ranked q
body: hey guys, does any1 else agree that findign a game in ranked takes to long, like honestly i was in q for 20 damn minutes! tell me if any1else has this problem, and can any1 gift me blood moon elise or blood moon kennen when he comes out both costing 975 rp? thx{{champion:60}}

replies.body:
Despite there being heaps of stuff being said around trying to get matchmaking times down, I can't seem to find any of it right now :/

On the other hand, nobody here is going to buy you a skin. Sorry kiddo ♥
